data.description: Welcome to your lakeside retreat! This charming log house is a haven for those seeking tranquility and a close connection with the great outdoors. Situated on the shores of popular Sunset Lake, this 3 bed 2+ bath home offers 100' lake frontage with dock . As you enter this charming home you get your first look at the water from the spacious foyer. Step inside, and you'll discover an interior that seamlessly combines rustic charm with many updates. The heart of the home is a living area, where a wood stove serves as a focal point, providing both warmth and an inviting gathering place full views of the lake. The stainless applianced kitchen, adjoining dining room and half bath w/ laundry completes the main level. Two bedrooms and bath on the 2nd fl. main house. The primary bedroom is 400 finished sq. ft. above the double garage or in the finished lower level with In Law options, patio, wood fired sauna, pellet stove and LVP flooring .Main heat 3 propane Rinnai heaters installed in 2021.
